official_title: A concurrent resolution authorizing the printing of the compilation entitled "Disclosure of the Corporate Ownership" as a Senate document.

summary.text: Provides that the compilation entitled "Disclosure of Corporate Ownership", prepared by the Subcommittees on Intergovernmental Relations and Budgeting, Management and Expenditures, of the Senate Committee on Government Operations, be printed with illustrations as a Senate document; and that there be printed five thousand (5,000) additional copies of such document for the use of that Committee. Authorizes the printing of 5,000 copies of the compilation entitled "Disclosure of Corporate Ownership" as a Senate document.
